name: Float32Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of Float32Array.

name: Float32Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 4 in the case of a Float32Array.

name: Float32Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Float32Array instances, the initial value is the Float32Array constructor.
